text: Louis-Jules Trochu (; 12 March 18157 October 1896) was a French military leader and politician. He served as President of the Government of National Defense—France's de facto head of state—from 4 September 1870 until his resignation on 22 January 1871. ==References== Category:1815 births Category:1896 deaths Category:Presidents of France Category:Prime ministers of France Category:People from Morbihan Category:Politicians from Brittany
